1. *Blizu* je parka. (It is close to the park.)
2. Njegova kuća je *blizu* tržnog centra. (His house is close to the shopping centre.)
3. Ona će biti *blizu* sutra. (She will be close tomorrow.)
4. Nisam *blizu*. (I am not close.)
5. Mogu li da dođem *blizu* tebe? (Can I come close to you?)
6. Njegov auto je *blizu* tebe. (His car is close to you.)
7. Ona je *blizu* mene. (She is close to me.)
8. Oni su *blizu* granice. (They are close to the border.)